  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/createml\/mllinearregressor\/modelparameters-swift.struct\/validation\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T13:57:21Z\n---\n\n# validation\n\n**Instance Property**\n\nValidation data.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar validation: MLLinearRegressor.ModelParameters.ValidationData { get set }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThe default is `.split(strategy: .automatic)`, which automatically generates the validation dataset from 0% to 10% of the training dataset.\n\n## Accessing parameters\n\n- **validationData**: Validation data represented as a `MLDataTable`.\n- **maxIterations**\n- **l1Penalty**\n- **l2Penalty**\n- **stepSize**\n- **convergenceThreshold**\n- **featureRescaling**\n\n",
